data.description: This great manufactured home sits on nearly an acre of land, offering the perfect blend of comfort, space & natural beauty. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms &1,782 SqFt of living space, this home provides a spacious & inviting atmosphere. This property comes with a massive shop that was built in 2000, designed specifically for Central OR toys. It features an enclosed lean-to & two huge bay doors, providing ample space for all your hobbies & storage needs. Whether you own an RV, are an avid outdoors person, or simply in need of a versatile workspace, this shop is a dream. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a circular driveway. The metal roof ensures durability & longevity. You'll find brand-new laminate flooring inside the home & the entire home has been tastefully painted. Step outside onto the deck, where you can relax & soak in the surroundings. Ideal location w/in easy reach of all the attractions La Pine offers. You'll have endless opportunities for outdoor adventures!
